txt.en: Wargs can be found patrolling the waste-lands in Arandor.\n\nYou should defeat wargs and pack-masters.
A bounty notice asks you to hunt the wargs patrolling around Arandor.

You have defeated pack-masters and other wargs in Arandor, fulfilling the bounty and ensuring safer travels on the road. The one who posted it should be pleased, but inwardly you wonder if Man will ever truly rule in Mordor, as he desired.

The bounty notice reads:

'Orcs and trolls are bad enough, but now the wargs have become emboldened and run down my soldiers even in broad daylight! Their leaders have no fear of Man, and by their example this new aggression spreads to the rest of the wargs in their pack.

'I'm asking for able-bodied fighters to hunt down and slay some of these stronger wargs. Let the pack know that Man still rules in Mordor!'
